《'''绽放'''》（{{lang-en|''Blossom''}}）是中国大陆拍摄青春励志片，导演吴祖云，主演姚星彤、顾琴烨。该片是“[[2008年夏季残疾人奥林匹克运动会|2008年夏季残疾人奥林匹克运动会]]”的献礼影片。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sn.xinhuanet.com/2008-09/16/content_14408045.htm|title=电影《绽放》为残奥会献礼|accessdate=2014-04-10|date=2008-09-16|work=新华网|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924103021/http://www.sn.xinhuanet.com/2008-09/16/content_14408045.htm|archivedate=2015-09-24}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.chinanews.com/olympic/news/2008/09-09/1376458.shtml |title=影片《绽放》演员姚星彤：扮演盲女让我更坚强 |date=2008-09-09 |accessdate=2008-09-09 |work=中国新闻网 |archive-date=2018-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180415190527/http://www.chinanews.com/olympic/news/2008/09-09/1376458.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>该片的原型人物是浙江省残疾人艺术团演员陈敏。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2008-05-26/14352037604.shtml|title=姚星彤谈《绽放》：盲人的心里有双明亮的眼睛|accessdate=2014-04-10|date=2008-05-26|work=新浪|archive-date=2018-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180415124949/http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2008-05-26/14352037604.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==剧情==
该片讲述了中国大陆正常人和残疾人互帮互助、互敬互爱的感人故事。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://gb.cri.cn/17844/2008/09/09/1425s2232987.htm|title=影片《绽放》为残奥会献礼 讲述盲女钢琴手故事|date=2008-09-09|work=国际在线|accessdate=2014-04-10|archive-date=2014-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413142727/http://gb.cri.cn/17844/2008/09/09/1425s2232987.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

